      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly car with plenty of life left for the right owner? This one isn\u2019t perfect, but it starts, runs, and offers a solid opportunity for someone who needs cheap transportation, a spare vehicle, or a project to tinker with. It\u2019s priced to reflect its age and wear, and with a little care it could be a very handy car. If you want something affordable and straightforward, this is worth a look.",
