      "description": "Built for the buyer who sees potential, this car has a seasoned, road-tested personality that gives it a story all its own. It starts conversations before it even leaves the driveway, with the kind of honest, lived-in character that makes it feel approachable and full of possibility. Perfect as a budget commuter, first project, or practical backup ride, it offers a chance to get behind the wheel without stretching your wallet. If you appreciate charm, usefulness, and the satisfaction of making something your own, this one is easy to root for.",
